				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-ng%C3%A2m/poem-4DAwE-zkYaCbjLMeL3c7mw">Bạch đầu ngâm - 白頭吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99i-Lan/D%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-m%C3%A3-h%C3%A0nh/poem-t0tPrjxez-niBXAx2E4uQw">Dưỡng mã hành - 養馬行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99i-Lan/author-Dt39a7a2bbyRe6i4iFJ_KQ">Lương Bội Lan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Tam-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-s%C6%A1n/poem-NTl089fj9a7qYQI1DzWmbg">Đề Tam Điệp sơn - 題三疊山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-nC6naBeYFtCN3Ft17XDeJw">Thiệu Trị hoàng đế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/Kim-ki%E1%BB%81u-c%E1%BA%A3m-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-wnsNlxFtLCrIjPDY_GZ-TQ">Kim kiều cảm sự - 金橋感事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-B%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-Th%C3%ADch-H%C3%A0o-Ch%C3%A2u-S%E1%BA%A7m-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BA%A5t-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-s%E1%BB%AD-Tham-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-oZgRt6bHZRvYsxtU3N2kaQ">Ký Bành Châu Cao tam thập ngũ sứ quân Thích, Hào Châu Sầm nhị thập thất trưởng sử Tham tam thập vận - 寄彭州高三十五使君適、虢州岑二十七長史參三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Li%E1%BB%85u-H%E1%BA%A1-Hu%E1%BB%87-m%E1%BB%99/poem-dXjsEHUOxEyEBhrQojVTZw">Liễu Hạ Huệ mộ - 柳下惠墓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%81u-B%E1%BB%95-Chi/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-o%C3%A1n/poem-GRSSI-PHn8LOX_d2OAWzMA">Phương Nghi oán - 芳儀怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%81u-B%E1%BB%95-Chi/author-sHoO5f0MU0Lsfjb4PEm2vg">Triều Bổ Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-MB-8C7oxGTS3aVFCIcY4Iw">Thuật hoài kỳ 4 - 述懷其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-5QO3Aqm4iu37_XSWPHCb1w">Tòng quân hành - 從軍行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/author-UC91PIpcFalgwS4PbK2Lpg">Dương Quýnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
